I seem to like to light myself on fire when welding under the vehicle for
any reason.  I can't see the flames with the helmet on so I use my sense of
smell and touch (not sure which one goes off first) to detect imminent doom.

Any way, now I have a leather apron and some welders sleeves (95% effective
except for hot metal balls that burn through the slevees (seems to keep
things exciting)).

